     1:1 sumewn petrov doulov kai apostolov ihsou
cristou toiv isotimon hmin lacousin pistin en dikaiosunh tou
yeou hmwn kai swthrov ihsou cristou
     1:2 cariv umin kai eirhnh plhyunyeih en epignwsei tou yeou
kai ihsou tou kuriou hmwn
     1:3 wv panta hmin thv yeiav dunamewv autou ta prov zwhn
kai eusebeian dedwrhmenhv dia thv epignwsewv tou kalesantov
hmav idia doxh kai areth 
     1:4 di wn ta timia hmin kai megista epaggelmata dedwrhtai
ina dia toutwn genhsye yeiav koinwnoi fusewv apofugontev thv
en tw kosmw en epiyumia fyorav
     1:5 kai auto touto de spoudhn pasan pareisenegkantev
epicorhghsate en th pistei umwn thn arethn en de th areth thn
gnwsin
     1:6 en de th gnwsei thn egkrateian en de th egkrateia thn
upomonhn en de th upomonh thn eusebeian
     1:7 en de th eusebeia thn filadelfian en de th filadelfia
thn agaphn
     1:8 tauta gar umin uparconta kai pleonazonta ouk argouv
oude akarpouv kayisthsin eiv thn tou kuriou hmwn ihsou cristou
epignwsin
     1:9 w gar mh parestin tauta tuflov estin muwpazwn lhyhn
labwn tou kayarismou twn palai autou amarthmatwn
     1:10 dio mallon adelfoi spoudasate bebaian umwn thn klhsin
kai ekloghn poieisyai tauta gar poiountev ou mh ptaishte pote
     1:11 outwv gar plousiwv epicorhghyhsetai umin h eisodov
eiv thn aiwnion basileian tou kuriou hmwn kai swthrov ihsou
cristou
     1:12 dio mellhsw aei umav upomimnhskein peri toutwn kaiper
eidotav kai esthrigmenouv en th paroush alhyeia
     1:13 dikaion de hgoumai ef oson eimi en toutw tw skhnwmati
diegeirein umav en upomnhsei
     1:14 eidwv oti tacinh estin h apoyesiv tou skhnwmatov mou
kaywv kai o kuriov hmwn ihsouv cristov edhlwsen moi
     1:15 spoudasw de kai ekastote ecein umav meta thn emhn
exodon thn toutwn mnhmhn poieisyai
     1:16 ou gar sesofismenoiv muyoiv exakolouyhsantev
egnwrisamen umin thn tou kuriou hmwn ihsou cristou dunamin kai
parousian all epoptai genhyentev thv ekeinou megaleiothtov
     1:17 labwn gar para yeou patrov timhn kai doxan fwnhv
enecyeishv autw toiasde upo thv megaloprepouv doxhv outov
estin o uiov mou o agaphtov eiv on egw eudokhsa
     1:18 kai tauthn thn fwnhn hmeiv hkousamen ex ouranou
enecyeisan sun autw ontev en tw orei tw agiw 
     1:19 kai ecomen bebaioteron ton profhtikon logon w kalwv
poieite prosecontev wv lucnw fainonti en aucmhrw topw ewv ou
hmera diaugash kai fwsforov anateilh en taiv kardiaiv umwn
     1:20 touto prwton ginwskontev oti pasa profhteia grafhv
idiav epilusewv ou ginetai
     1:21 ou gar yelhmati anyrwpou hnecyh pote profhteia alla 
upo pneumatov agiou feromenoi elalhsan apo yeou anyrwpoi
     2:1 egenonto de kai qeudoprofhtai en tw law wv kai en umin
esontai qeudodidaskaloi oitinev pareisaxousin aireseiv apwleiav
kai ton agorasanta autouv despothn arnoumenoi epagontev eautoiv
tacinhn apwleian
     2:2 kai polloi exakolouyhsousin autwn taiv aselgeiaiv di
ouv h odov thv alhyeiav blasfhmhyhsetai
     2:3 kai en pleonexia plastoiv logoiv umav emporeusontai
oiv to krima ekpalai ouk argei kai h apwleia autwn ou nustazei
     2:4 ei gar o yeov aggelwn amarthsantwn ouk efeisato alla 
siroiv zofou tartarwsav paredwken eiv krisin throumenouv
     2:5 kai arcaiou kosmou ouk efeisato alla ogdoon nwe
dikaiosunhv khruka efulaxen kataklusmon kosmw asebwn epaxav
     2:6 kai poleiv sodomwn kai gomorrav tefrwsav katastrofh
katekrinen upodeigma mellontwn asebein teyeikwv
     2:7 kai dikaion lwt kataponoumenon upo thv twn ayesmwn en
aselgeia anastrofhv errusato
     2:8 blemmati gar kai akoh o dikaiov enkatoikwn en
autoiv hmeran ex hmerav quchn dikaian anomoiv ergoiv ebasanizen
     2:9 oiden kuriov eusebeiv ek peirasmwn ruesyai adikouv de
eiv hmeran krisewv kolazomenouv threin
     2:10 malista de touv opisw sarkov en epiyumia miasmou
poreuomenouv kai kuriothtov katafronountav tolmhtai auyadeiv
doxav ou tremousin blasfhmountev
     2:11 opou aggeloi iscui kai dunamei meizonev ontev ou
ferousin kat autwn para kuriw blasfhmon krisin
     2:12 outoi de wv aloga zwa gegennhmena fusika eiv alwsin
kai fyoran en oiv agnoousin blasfhmountev en th fyora autwn kai
fyarhsontai
     2:13 komioumenoi misyon adikiav hdonhn hgoumenoi thn en
hmera trufhn spiloi kai mwmoi entrufwntev en taiv apataiv autwn
suneuwcoumenoi umin
     2:14 ofyalmouv econtev mestouv moicalidov kai akatapaustouv 
amartiav deleazontev qucav asthriktouv kardian
gegumnasmenhn pleonexiav econtev katarav tekna
     2:15 kataleipontev euyeian odon eplanhyhsan
exakolouyhsantev th odw tou balaam tou bosor ov misyon adikiav
hgaphsen
     2:16 elegxin de escen idiav paranomiav upozugion afwnon en
anyrwpou fwnh fyegxamenon ekwlusen thn tou profhtou parafronian
     2:17 outoi eisin phgai anudroi kai omiclai upo lailapov
elaunomenai oiv o zofov tou skotouv tethrhtai
     2:18 uperogka gar mataiothtov fyeggomenoi deleazousin en
epiyumiaiv sarkov aselgeiaiv touv oligwv apofeugontav touv en
planh anastrefomenouv
     2:19 eleuyerian autoiv epaggellomenoi autoi douloi
uparcontev thv fyorav w gar tiv htthtai toutw dedoulwtai
     2:20 ei gar apofugontev ta miasmata tou kosmou en
epignwsei tou kuriou hmwn kai swthrov ihsou cristou
toutoiv de palin emplakentev httwntai gegonen autoiv ta escata
ceirona twn prwtwn
     2:21 kreisson gar hn autoiv mh epegnwkenai thn odon thv
dikaiosunhv h epignousin upostreqai ek thv paradoyeishv autoiv
agiav entolhv
     2:22 sumbebhken autoiv to thv alhyouv paroimiav kuwn
epistreqav epi to idion exerama kai uv lousamenh eiv kulismon
borborou
     3:1 tauthn hdh agaphtoi deuteran umin grafw epistolhn en
aiv diegeirw umwn en upomnhsei thn eilikrinh dianoian
     3:2 mnhsyhnai twn proeirhmenwn rhmatwn upo twn agiwn
profhtwn kai thv twn apostolwn umwn entolhv tou kuriou kai
swthrov
     3:3 touto prwton ginwskontev oti eleusontai ep escatwn twn
hmerwn en empaigmonh empaiktai kata tav idiav autwn
epiyumiav poreuomenoi
     3:4 kai legontev pou estin h epaggelia thv parousiav autou
af hv gar oi paterev ekoimhyhsan panta outwv diamenei ap archv
ktisewv
     3:5 lanyanei gar autouv touto yelontav oti ouranoi hsan
ekpalai kai gh ex udatov kai di udatov sunestwsa tw tou yeou
logw
     3:6 di wn o tote kosmov udati kataklusyeiv apwleto
     3:7 oi de nun ouranoi kai h gh tw autw logw
teyhsaurismenoi eisin puri throumenoi eiv hmeran krisewv kai
apwleiav twn asebwn anyrwpwn
     3:8 en de touto mh lanyanetw umav agaphtoi oti mia hmera
para kuriw wv cilia eth kai cilia eth wv hmera mia
     3:9 ou bradunei kuriov thv epaggeliav wv tinev braduthta
hgountai alla makroyumei di umav mh boulomenov tinav apolesyai
alla pantav eiv metanoian cwrhsai
     3:10 hxei de hmera kuriou wv klepthv en h oi ouranoi
roizhdon pareleusontai stoiceia de kausoumena luyhsetai kai gh
kai ta en auth erga katakahsetai
     3:11 toutwn oun pantwn luomenwn potapouv dei uparcein
umav en agiaiv anastrofaiv kai eusebeiaiv
     3:12 prosdokwntav kai speudontav thn parousian thv tou
yeou hmerav di hn ouranoi puroumenoi luyhsontai kai stoiceia
kausoumena thketai
     3:13 kainouv de ouranouv kai kainhn ghn kata ta 
epaggelmata autou prosdokwmen en oiv dikaiosunh katoikei
     3:14 dio agaphtoi tauta prosdokwntev spoudasate aspiloi
kai amwmhtoi autw eureyhnai en eirhnh
     3:15 kai thn tou kuriou hmwn makroyumian swthrian hgeisye
kaywv kai o agaphtov hmwn adelfov paulov kata thn doyeisan autw
sofian egraqen umin
     3:16 wv kai en pasaiv taiv epistolaiv lalwn en autaiv peri
toutwn en aiv estin dusnohta tina a oi amayeiv kai asthriktoi
streblousin wv kai tav loipav grafav prov thn idian autwn
apwleian
     3:17 umeiv oun agaphtoi proginwskontev fulassesye ina mh
th twn ayesmwn planh sunapacyentev ekpeshte tou idiou sthrigmou
     3:18 auxanete de en cariti kai gnwsei tou kuriou hmwn kai
swthrov ihsou cristou autw h doxa kai nun kai eiv hmeran aiwnov
